data.description: GORGEOUS MT ZION Fixer Upper-Over 3000 Sq. Ft.--Large concrete front porch welcomes you into the raised living room, sunken firepit area with custom couch, 2 sided fireplace with views from living room and Firepit area. Beautiful kitchen, with bedroom on main floor could also be used as a private office, home school room, or more. There is a nice 3/4 bath on the main floor. Upstairs are 3 nice sized bedroom, 2 full baths including the Master Bath. Rec room in basement. Selling as-is, needs some repairs, but this is a fabulous home. Room sizes are estimates, will be professionally measured soon. Great location, on a quiet cul-de-sac--FABULOUS neighbors. Seller has lived in this home for over 20 years. Great family home. HURRY on this one, when fixed up, should be worth over $300K.
